main_text: Smart home systems have multiple standards. This solution combines all of them in one, allowing for control and visualization of all of your smart home devices from different vendors.
benefits: Visualize and control all of your smart home equipment with just one controllerMultiple vendorsMultiple standards
Extendable for multi-purpose applications and radio PHYs
